{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"7cb94e100fc1bf9e3c0afd83c7bc2293e879fc1014372198313c837405101b15","slug":"decompression","location":"/handbook/health/decompression.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"系统减负：外化、传递与信任","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/handbook/health/decompression.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/handbook/health/decompression.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"decompression.md","url":"/decompression-75767e65d66499743d6be147da44e133.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根据“情绪卸载 → 责任剥离 → 机制建设 → 沟通降耗 → 制度自信”的系统化减负逻辑，对这组卡片的表述进行了优化。重点在于建立外部系统来承接内部压力。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"f7YmJQem4d"}],"key":"KRaH4OwkOs"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把负面情绪外包给“第二大脑”","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"qJKgbkYmJ8"}],"identifier":"id","label":"把负面情绪外包给“第二大脑”","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"GeMwoXGsAL"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：周末关掉工作软件后，内心依然感到害怕和混乱。此时，文档成了最好的容器，接住了这些无处安放的情绪。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"UPKoiVBsOk"}],"key":"FS0RsdHtmf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：不要让大脑独自消化情绪。当感到无力或焦虑时，打开一个文档或录音笔，说：“现在有一份害怕，请你先接着。”书写的动作即是外包，把情绪从“内存”移到“硬盘”，让大脑重获自由。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"ciLhYcsxiF"}],"key":"Qr2V77YyNV"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把个人大脑的内容迁移到公司大脑，主动减轻责任","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"T20tcIxKue"}],"identifier":"id","label":"把个人大脑的内容迁移到公司大脑，主动减轻责任","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"AbwEazESVB"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：将个人第二大脑的内容大幅迁移至公司系统后，不仅团队有了章程，自己更感到“责任轻了许多”。原来责任的重量可以通过载体的转移而减轻。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"KkX6mypgGy"}],"key":"HQgkkhAW4E"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：定期审计个人大脑。识别那些“本该由团队或系统承接”的事项，主动迁移出去。每迁移一项，就对自己确认一遍：“我的责任又轻了一点。”这不仅是放权，更是为了让自己回归更轻盈的角色。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"mMq6CYO6B9"}],"key":"tWMt63dtvk"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把认知能力通过平台传递，减少个人消耗","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"F3Vvj1qeN7"}],"identifier":"id","label":"把认知能力通过平台传递，减少个人消耗","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"iTGpVq1moU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：认知若只停留在脑子里，只能靠“人肉”推动；一旦上了平台，就具备了自我生长的影响力。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"yI89rXgEHm"}],"key":"rT7GIThsXu"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：拒绝做“复读机”。遇到需要反复解释、推动的事项，停下来问：“这能不能写成一份平台指南？”把“重复消耗”转化为“一次性建设”。以后每次有人问，只需指向平台，让系统替你说话。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"pSHfl4FfrQ"}],"key":"Jw7RpzE74h"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把思考同步给团队，但不push任何人去跟","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"tcIXAQsPvo"}],"identifier":"id-push","label":"把思考同步给团队，但不push任何人去跟","html_id":"id-push","implicit":true,"key":"uQCCB6sW8O"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：把思考过程公开透明地同步出去，大家想看就看，反馈反而更真实。这种“不推不压”的方式，意外地让沟通变得解压。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"hU9RizBh1b"}],"key":"WEhXcfZSm9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：建立“广播式沟通”机制。把想法写成文档放在公共区，只发一条轻量的通知：“这是我的思考，有兴趣可阅。”把选择权交给对方，尊重他人的自由，也保护自己的情绪不被“说服他人”的阻力所消耗。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"mf8pxEoTIQ"}],"key":"LkFdl7IfBM"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用对制度的信心来替代对惩罚的担忧","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"Z8U83YYO2a"}],"identifier":"id","label":"用对制度的信心来替代对惩罚的担忧","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"nyWdCoihGR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：以前不敢碰的“罚钱机制”，现在因为有了细致\n透明的标准，变得不再可怕。意识到“我不担心罚跑人”，这其实是对制度成熟度的自信。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"ofuGf1yyMJ"}],"key":"rzl0mJOBAp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：在推行严厉制度前，先检查标准是否“明确、细致、透明”。如果是，就相信标准本身的力量。用“对制度的信心”去覆盖“对后果的担忧”，不再内耗于“别人会怎么想”，让规则回归中性。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"i7s6jWJh1V"}],"key":"K3AXVDh0aG"}],"key":"QEYRKbrfOy"}],"key":"JvcIA7NxiM"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}